import axios from 'axios'; import React, { useState } from 'react'; import { Link, useNavigate } from 'react-router-dom'; import Swal from 'sweetalert2'; function Signup() { const [name, setname] = useState(''); const [email, setemail] = useState(''); const [pass, setpass] = useState(''); const [type, settype] = useState(''); const navigate = useNavigate(); const insertrecord = async() => { if(name == "") { Swal.fire({ title: "Validation Message", text: "Name Field iS Required*", icon: "wrong" }); } else if (email === "" || !email.includes("@")) { Swal.fire({ title: "Validation Message", text: "Please enter a valid email address", icon: "error" }); } else if (!/^(?=.*[a-zA-Z])(?=.*\d)(?=.*[@$!%*?&])[A-Za-z\d@$!%*?&]{3,}$/.test(pass)) { Swal.fire({ title: "Validation Message", text: "Password must contain at least 3 letters, 3 numbers, and 1 special character", icon: "error" }); } else { const res = await fetch("http://localhost:4000",{ method: 'POST', headers : { 'Content-Type' : 'application/json' }, body : JSON.stringify({name, email ,pass,type}) }) let data = await res.json(); console.log(data); if(data.success) { navigate('/login') } // axios.post('http://localhost:4000',{name,email,pass,type}) // navigate('/login'); } } return(
